cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

This paper proposes a method for enhancing video quality through frame interpolation and reducing motion blur. These tasks are commonly addressed in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. The paper also discusses the use of a pyramid module and recurrent module, which are common techniques in graphics (cs.GR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research.
